{
  "stem": "26983.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which we later on, as I told you, could--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or from the other sources, from Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyhow--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not anymore--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were not anymore in the category of normal human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were something extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they knew they would be killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they had prepared a kind of uprising.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember in the straw of Kalman's mattress, there was a-- something how you call-- a little--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A kind of little bayonet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he stole and had it prepared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it didn't help him much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw when I went to this crematorium number 2, also the place where Mengele made his vivisection.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This table from stone, with a special place where blood could drain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw, of course, an empty box of wood, where they were usually collecting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It said go in peace, which were later melted and sent I think to the German [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was such a box about how much it could be, 60 on 40 and 40.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the sauna, which was next to it, we also worked, of course, with our roll wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there I saw tremendous huge section with human hair, which were prepared to send off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They also collected this hair, a tremendous lot of hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, in the sauna, we little children could go in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was staying sometimes a whole transport of 2,000 naked women, waiting at least.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't know if they go to gas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they were in the sauna, which means the had a little chance maybe to go to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was one of our jobs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes the clothes, sometimes from the crematorium we usually took the wood for normal, so-called normal use for heating.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
